tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif Lam Mim Sad"
  7,7,"and We shall relate to them with knowledge; assuredly We were not absent."
  7,9,"and he whose scales are light -- they have lost their soul for wronging Our signs."
  7,10,"We have established you in the earth and there appointed for you livelihood; little thanks you show."